c: 9
v: 120
t: "Zvakanga zvisina kunaka kuti vanhu vemuMadinah uye maA’raab (vagari vekumaruwa) vemunharaunda kuti vasare kumashure kwamutumwa waAllah (Muhammad (SAW) pakurwa munzira yaAllah), uye kushuvira hupenyu hwavo kuhupenyu hwake. Nokuti havana kushupika nenyota kana kuneta kana nzara munzira yaAllah, kana kutora chinhanho chokusumudza hasha dzevasingatendi, kana kuisa marwadzo kuvavengi asi zvaitonyorwa kwavari sebasa rakanaka. Zvirokwazvo, Allah havatambisi mibairo yevatsvene"